msgid ""
"Filters with the same group key will be ORed together within the group, "
"while different filter groups will be ANDed together. Undefined group "
"keys are treated as unique groups, i.e. are not grouped together. For "
"example, if a table has three filters, of which two are for departments "
"Finance and Marketing (group key = 'department'), and one refers to the "
"region Europe (group key = 'region'), the filter clause would apply the "
"filter (department = 'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND (region ="
" 'Europe')."
msgstr ""
"Filtri ar vienu grupas atslēgu tiks apvienoti ar OR grupas ietvaros, bet "
"dažādas filtru grupas tiks apvienotas ar AND. Nedefinētas grupas atslēgas"
" tiek uzskatītas par unikālām grupām, t.i., netiek grupētas kopā. "
"Piemēram, ja tabulai ir trīs filtri, no kuriem divi ir departamentiem "
"Finanses un Mārketings (grupas atslēga = 'department'), un viens attiecas"
" uz reģionu Eiropa (grupas atslēga = 'region'), filtra nosacījums "
"piemērotu filtru (department = 'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND"
" (region = 'Europe')."

